        "desc": "Mother's elongated sinewy arm arcing diagonally from the upper-left quadrant down toward the center-right, rendered in fluid liquid brushstrokes of dusty rose and sepia. Fraying edges dissolve into surrounding haze. Fingers splayed open, reaching rightward toward the child, fingertips nearly meeting the central void."
      },
