        "type": "obj",
        "desc": "Smudged silhouette of a small child figure anchored in the lower-right quadrant, only partially formed. Soft charcoal-and-sepia smudge suggesting head and torso, one outstretched arm reaching leftward and upward toward the mother. Edges feather into the muted background."
      },
